The dataset contains thousands sales from a unknown e-commerce in 2019. I got from my data science course so I saved here to learning material

The dataset dictionary:
1. Order ID = Order id each rows 
2. Product = Product name

4. Price Each = Price each product 
5. Order Date = Date of sales order 
6. Purchase Address = Address of people who ordered 
7. City = City 
8. Postal Code = Postal Code
